== 反响 ==
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於242個專業評論有25%的新鮮度，平均得分4.2/10<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fifty_shades_of_grey/ | title=Fifty Shades of Grey | work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]] | accessdate=2015-03-02 | archive-date=2015-11-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151103215023/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fifty_shades_of_grey/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上根據46篇影評，得分46，[[IMDB|IMDB]]得分4.1，評價褒貶不一<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/fifty-shades-of-grey | title=Fifty Shades of Grey Reviews | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=2015-03-02 | archive-date=2015-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124063345/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/fifty-shades-of-grey | dead-url=no }}</ref>；[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]上观众评分C+，口碑不佳。

